West Alto Bonito first appeared as a [[census designated place]] under the name '''Alto Bonito''' in the [[2000 U.S. census]].<ref name=2000CensusTX/> The name was changed to '''West Alto Bonito''' in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusTX/>

